---
canvas: 400x400
bg: #0f172a
fps: 24
---

# Star mask on image using parametric xt
image photo "image.jpg" w:300 h:300 | 0s - 4s
  x: 200
  y: 200
  mask: xt("200 + (80 + 50 * cos(t * 5)) * cos(t)", "200 + (80 + 50 * cos(t * 5)) * sin(t)", 0, 6.28, 100)

text label "Star Mask on Image" font:Roboto size:18 fill:#fff | 0s - 4s
  x: 200
  y: 360
